data.description: Welcome to a world of comfort and tranquility! Nestled on a spacious half-acre lot, this captivating 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom modular home beckons you with open arms. Step inside to discover a haven meticulously designed to embrace modern living and elevate your lifestyle. With four cozy bedrooms, everyone can have their own personal retreat. The two immaculate bathrooms add convenience and elegance to your daily routine. Embrace the possibilities that come with a generous half-acre lot. Call now!
